data.description: This charming ranch-style home is nestled in a tranquil cul-de-sac of the desirable neighborhood of Carter's Cove. With three bedrooms, two bathrooms, a large living room, a dining room, a beautifully updated kitchen, and a light-filled sunroom, this home is designed for comfortable living and effortless entertainment. The front porch and the sunroom offer a picturesque setting for outdoor enjoyment, overlooking the serene, wooded lot. Further enhancing this home's appeal is the oversized detached 2-car garage, equipped with electricity and a full attic. This home provides all the space and privacy you need for peaceful living. Carter’s Cove offers a pool, clubhouse & recreation facilities if you join the association.
